<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="color-scheme" content="light only">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#FFFFFF">
<title>김지예 — Architectural Designer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#FFFFFF;
    --ink:#141414;
    --sub:#5C5C5C;
    --line:#E5E5E3;
    --muted:#A0A0A0;
  }
  *{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; color-scheme: light only; background:var(--bg); }
  body{
    background:var(--bg) !important; color:var(--ink) !important;
    font-family:'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; font-weight:300;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    min-height:100vh;
  }
  a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
  ::selection{ background:var(--ink); color:var(--bg); }
  :focus-visible{ outline:2px solid var(--ink); outline-offset:3px; }
  button{ font-family:inherit; }

  .wrap{ max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding-left:8vw; padding-right:8vw; }
  @media (min-width:1300px){ .wrap{ padding-left:120px; padding-right:120px; } }

  h1,h2,h3{ font-family:'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }
  .eyebrow{
    font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.22em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted); font-weight:500;
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{ content:""; width:20px; height:1px; background:var(--muted); display:inline-block; }

  /* ---------- COVER ---------- */
  html.cover-lock, body.cover-lock{ overflow:hidden; height:100%; }
  .cover{
    position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:999; background:var(--bg);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:28px 8vw 40px; cursor:pointer;
    opacity:1; visibility:visible; transition:opacity .55s ease, visibility .55s ease;
  }
  @media (min-width:1300px){ .cover{ padding:32px 120px 48px; } }
  .cover.cover-hidden{ opacity:0; visibility:hidden; pointer-events:none; }
  .cover-top{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between;
    font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted); font-weight:400;
  }
  .cover-main{ flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:28px; text-align:center; }
  .cover-blank{
    font-weight:300; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;
    font-size:clamp(44px,10vw,110px); color:var(--ink);
  }
  .cover-blank .bracket{ font-weight:400; color:var(--ink); }
  .cover-blank .word{ color:var(--muted); font-style:italic; font-weight:600; }
  .cover-sub{
    font-size:12px; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);
  }
  .cover-enter{
    align-self:flex-end; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    background:none; border:1px solid var(--ink); border-radius:100px;
    padding:12px 22px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit;
    font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:700;
    color:var(--ink); transition:background .25s ease, color .25s ease;
  }
  .cover-enter svg{ width:13px; height:13px; transition:transform .25s ease; }
  .cover-enter:hover{ background:var(--ink); color:#fff; }
  .cover-enter:hover svg{ transform:translateY(2px); }

  /* ---------- TOP BAR ---------- */
  header.topbar{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .topbar-inner{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:18px 8vw;
  }
  @media (min-width:1300px){ .topbar-inner{ padding:18px 120px; } }
  .topbar-inner .brand{
    font-weight:700; font-size:17px; white-space:nowrap;
    background:none; border:none; padding:0; cursor:pointer;
    font-family:inherit; color:var(--ink); transition:opacity .2s ease;
  }
  .topbar-inner .brand:hover{ opacity:0.6; }
  .topbar-inner .brand span{ color:var(--muted); font-weight:500; font-size:11px; margin-left:8px; letter-spacing:0.05em;}

  /* ---------- ICON NAV ---------- */
  nav.icon-nav{
    display:flex; gap:4px; overflow-x:auto; scrollbar-width:none;
  }
  nav.icon-nav::-webkit-scrollbar{ display:none; }
  .nav-item{
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px;
    background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; padding:10px 16px;
    color:var(--muted); flex-shrink:0; border-radius:10px; transition:background .25s ease, color .25s ease;
  }
  .nav-item svg{ width:19px; height:19px; stroke:var(--muted); transition:stroke .25s ease, transform .25s ease; }
  .nav-item span{ font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:700; }
  .nav-item:hover{ color:var(--ink); background:#F7F7F5; }
  .nav-item:hover svg{ stroke:var(--ink); transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .nav-item.active{ color:var(--ink); }
  .nav-item.active svg{ stroke:var(--ink); }
  .nav-item.active::after{
    content:""; width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--ink); margin-top:1px;
  }
  .nav-item:not(.active)::after{ content:""; width:4px; height:4px; margin-top:1px; }

  /* ---------- HERO (always visible) ---------- */
  section.hero{ padding:64px 8vw 56px; }
  @media (min-width:1300px){ section.hero{ padding:72px 120px 64px; } }
  section.hero .eyebrow{ margin-bottom:28px; }
  section.hero h1{
    font-weight:700; font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,60px); line-height:1.18; letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    max-width:900px;
  }
  section.hero h1 em{ font-style:normal; font-weight:900; }
  section.hero .sub{
    margin-top:24px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.75; color:var(--sub);
    max-width:460px; font-weight:300;
  }

  /* ---------- VIEW SWITCH ---------- */
  .view{ display:none; }
  .view.active{ display:block; animation:fadeIn .35s ease; }
  @keyframes fadeIn{ from{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(6px);} to{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);} }

  section.block{ padding:72px 8vw 96px; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  @media (min-width:1300px){ section.block{ padding:80px 120px 110px; } }
  .block-head{ display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:flex-end; margin-bottom:48px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; }
  .block-head h2{ font-size:clamp(26px,3.2vw,38px); font-weight:700; }

  /* ---------- PROFILE ---------- */
  .profile-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:200px 1fr; gap:48px; align-items:start; }
  @media (max-width:840px){ .profile-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:32px; } }
  .profile-photo{
    width:100%; max-width:200px; aspect-ratio:3/4;
    border:1px solid var(--line); overflow:hidden; background:#FAFAF9;
  }
  .profile-photo img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; }
  .profile-left{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:24px; width:100%; max-width:200px; }
  .profile-mini-facts{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; }
  .profile-mini-facts dt{ font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color:var(--muted); text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:4px; font-weight:700; }
  .profile-mini-facts dd{ font-size:12px; color:var(--sub); font-weight:400; line-height:1.5; }
  @media (min-width:841px){
    .profile-text{ margin-left:auto; max-width:560px; }
  }
  .profile-text p{ font-size:16px; line-height:1.9; color:var(--sub); font-weight:300; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .profile-text p:last-child{ margin-bottom:0; }
  .profile-text p strong{ color:var(--ink); font-weight:700; }

  /* ---- compact summary widgets inside profile ---- */
  .mini-widgets{ margin-top:56px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:1px; background:var(--line); border:1px solid var(--line); isolation:isolate; position:relative; z-index:1; }
  @media (max-width:900px){ .mini-widgets{ grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
  .mini-card{ background:#fff; padding:20px; }
  .mini-card-head{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .mini-card-head h4{ font-weight:700; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); }
  .mini-list{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:11px; }
  .mini-row{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px; font-size:12px; }
  .mini-row .m-year{ color:var(--muted); font-weight:700; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.03em; }
  .mini-row .m-title{ color:var(--ink); font-weight:400; line-height:1.4; }

  .mini-row-career{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px; font-size:12px; }
  .mini-row-career .m-year{ color:var(--muted); font-weight:700; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.03em; flex-shrink:0; padding-top:1px; }
  .mini-row-career .m-right{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-end; text-align:right; gap:3px; }
  .mini-row-career .m-company{ color:var(--ink); font-weight:400; line-height:1.4; }
  .mini-row-career .m-position{ color:var(--muted); font-weight:500; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.03em; }

  .skill-row{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:5px; font-size:11px; }
  .skill-row .s-label{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-weight:700; color:var(--sub); }
  .skill-dots{ display:flex; gap:3px; }
  .skill-dots span{ width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--line); }
  .skill-dots span.filled{ background:var(--muted); }

  .skills-panel{ margin-top:1px; background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--line); border-top:none; padding:20px; }
  .skills-panel .mini-card-head{ margin-bottom:16px; }
  .skills-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(5, 1fr); gap:16px 16px; }
  @media (max-width:900px){ .skills-grid{ grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width:560px){ .skills-grid{ grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr); } }

  /* ---------- PROJECT SUB-TABS ---------- */
  .subtabs{ display:flex; gap:8px; margin-bottom:48px; }
  .subtab-btn{
    background:none; border:1px solid var(--line); padding:10px 20px; font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:0.05em; color:var(--muted); cursor:pointer; border-radius:100px; transition:all .2s ease;
    font-weight:700;
  }
  .subtab-btn.active{ background:var(--ink); color:#fff; border-color:var(--ink); }
  .subview{ display:none; }
  .subview.active{ display:block; }

  /* ---------- PROJECTS (row list, image + text) ---------- */
  .project-row-list{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
  .project-row-item{
    display:flex; gap:24px; width:100%; text-align:left;
    padding:28px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    background:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;
    cursor:pointer; align-items:flex-start; font-family:inherit;
    color:var(--ink); -webkit-appearance:none; appearance:none;
  }
  .project-row-list .project-row-item:last-child{ border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .pr-thumb{
    width:170px; height:auto; display:block; flex-shrink:0;
    border:1px solid var(--line); transition:opacity .25s ease;
  }
  .project-row-item:hover .pr-thumb{ opacity:0.85; }
  .pr-body{ flex:1; min-width:0; }
  .pr-year{ font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:var(--muted); }
  .pr-body h3{ font-size:19px; font-weight:700; margin-top:6px; color:var(--ink); transition:color .25s ease; }
  .project-row-item:hover .pr-body h3{ color:var(--sub); }
  .pr-tag{ font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); margin-top:6px; display:block; font-weight:700; }
  .pr-desc{ font-size:13px; line-height:1.75; color:var(--sub); font-weight:300; margin-top:10px; display:none; }
  @media (min-width:641px){ .pr-desc{ display:block; } }
  @media (max-width:640px){
    .project-row-item{ flex-direction:column; gap:14px; }
    .pr-thumb{ width:100%; height:auto; }
  }

  /* ---------- PROJECT DETAIL MODAL (carousel) ---------- */
  .proj-modal{
    position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:900; background:rgba(20,20,20,0.6);
    display:none; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:center;
    overflow-y:auto; padding:40px 16px;
  }
  .proj-modal.proj-modal-open{ display:flex; }
  .proj-modal-panel{
    background:#fff; max-width:640px; width:100%; margin:0 auto;
    border:1px solid var(--line); position:relative;
  }
  .pm-topbar{
    display:flex; justify-content:flex-end; align-items:center;
    padding:10px 14px;
  }
  .proj-modal-close{
    background:none; border:none; padding:4px; cursor:pointer;
    font-size:18px; line-height:1; color:var(--ink);
  }
  .pm-stage{ position:relative; background:#F5F5F4; aspect-ratio:4/3; overflow:hidden; }
  .pm-stage img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:contain; display:block; cursor:zoom-in; }

  /* ---------- FULLSCREEN IMAGE LIGHTBOX (pinch/scroll to zoom) ---------- */
  .img-lightbox{
    position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:950; background:#000;
    display:none; overflow:auto; touch-action:pinch-zoom;
  }
  .img-lightbox.lightbox-open{ display:block; }
  .img-lightbox-inner{
    min-height:100%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:0;
  }
  .img-lightbox img{ display:block; width:100%; height:auto; }
  .lightbox-close{
    position:fixed; top:14px; right:16px; z-index:2;
    background:none; border:none; padding:6px; cursor:pointer;
    font-size:22px; line-height:1; color:#fff;
  }
  .pm-controls{
    display:flex; justify-content:flex-end; align-items:center;
    padding:10px 14px;
  }
  .pm-arrow{
    background:none; border:none; padding:4px; cursor:pointer; color:var(--ink);
    display:flex; align-items:center;
  }
  .pm-arrow svg{ width:34px; height:14px; }
  .proj-modal-text{ padding:24px 26px 32px; }
  .proj-modal-tag{ font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); font-weight:700; }
  .proj-modal-text h2{ font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin-top:10px; }
  .proj-modal-desc{ font-size:14px; line-height:1.8; color:var(--sub); font-weight:300; margin-top:14px; }
  html.modal-lock, body.modal-lock{ overflow:hidden; height:100%; }

  .other-works{ margin-top:64px; }
  .other-works h4{ font-weight:700; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:20px; color:var(--sub); }
  .ow-year-group{ margin-bottom:36px; }
  .ow-year-group:last-child{ margin-bottom:0; }
  .ow-year-label{
    font-family:'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:20px; color:var(--ink);
    padding-bottom:8px; margin-bottom:16px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .ow-grid{ column-count:2; column-gap:48px; }
  @media (max-width:760px){ .ow-grid{ column-count:1; } }
  .ow-row{
    break-inside: avoid; -webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;
    padding:14px 0;
    display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .ow-row .ow-year{ font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:var(--muted); flex-shrink:0; width:26px; }
  .ow-row .ow-body{ flex:1; min-width:0; }
  .ow-row .ow-title{ font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); display:block; }
  .ow-row .ow-desc{ font-size:11px; font-weight:300; color:var(--muted); display:block; margin-top:3px; }

  .extra-note{
    margin-top:56px; padding-top:32px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    font-size:13px; color:var(--sub); font-weight:300; line-height:1.8;
  }
  .extra-note strong{ color:var(--ink); font-weight:700; }

  /* ---------- PHOTO GALLERY ---------- */
  .photo-intro{ font-size:14px; line-height:1.8; color:var(--sub); font-weight:300; max-width:520px; margin-bottom:48px; }
  .photo-grid{ column-count:3; column-gap:14px; }
  @media (max-width:900px){ .photo-grid{ column-count:2; } }
  @media (max-width:560px){ .photo-grid{ column-count:1; } }
  .photo-item{ break-inside:avoid; -webkit-column-break-inside:avoid; margin-bottom:28px; }
  .photo-item img{ width:100%; display:block; border:1px solid var(--line); }
  .photo-item .cap{ font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:8px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.02em; }
  .photo-set-label{ font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); margin:40px 0 16px; }
  .photo-set-label:first-child{ margin-top:0; }

  /* ---------- CONTACT VIEW ---------- */
  .contact-view h2{ font-size:clamp(28px,4.4vw,48px); font-weight:700; max-width:640px; line-height:1.3; }
  .contact-row{ margin-top:44px; display:flex; gap:48px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .contact-row div dt{ font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color:var(--muted); text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:8px; font-weight:700; }
  .contact-row div dd{ font-size:15px; font-weight:400; }
  .contact-row div dd a{ border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink); padding-bottom:1px; }
  .contact-row div dd a:hover{ color:var(--muted); border-color:var(--muted); }

  .ig-row{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }

  /* ---------- PERSISTENT FOOTER ---------- */
  footer.site-foot{
    padding:24px 8vw; border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;
    font-weight:500;
  }
  @media (min-width:1300px){ footer.site-foot{ padding:24px 120px; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cover" id="coverScreen">
  <div class="cover-top">
    <span>Architectural Portfolio</span>
    <span>2019 — 2026</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-main">
    <div class="cover-blank"><span class="bracket">[</span> <span class="word">BLANK</span> <span class="bracket">]</span></div>
    <p class="cover-sub">Kim Ji Ye · Selected Works 2019 – 2026</p>
  </div>
  <button class="cover-enter" id="coverEnterBtn" aria-label="포트폴리오 보기">
    <span>Enter</span>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
  </button>
</div>

<header class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-inner">
    <button class="brand" id="brandReturnBtn" type="button">김지예 KIM JI YE <span>ARCHITECTURAL DESIGNER</span></button>
  </div>
  <nav class="icon-nav wrap" id="iconNav">
    <button class="nav-item active" data-view="profile" aria-current="page">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8s8 3.6 8 8"/></svg>
      <span>Profile</span>
    </button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="projects">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/></svg>
      <span>Projects</span>
    </button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="photo">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3.5"/><path d="M8 6l1.5-2.5h5L16 6"/></svg>
      <span>Photo</span>
    </button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="contact">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="1.5"/><path d="m4 6.5 8 6 8-6"/></svg>
      <span>Contact</span>
    </button>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO (always visible) -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Architectural Portfolio — 2019 – 2026</div>
  <h1>빈 공간이 아닌<br><em>채워질 가능성</em>을 만들다</h1>
  <p class="sub">보이드와 매스, 빛과 그림자의 관계를 통해 사용자의 경험을 설계합니다. 절제된 언어로 공간의 본질에 다가갑니다.</p>
</section>

<main class="wrap" style="padding-left:0; padding-right:0;">

<!-- PROFILE (includes Awards / Career / License as mini sections) -->
<div class="view active" id="view-profile">
  <section class="block" style="border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
    <div class="block-head block-head--profile">
      <h2>Profile</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-grid">
      <div class="profile-left">
        <div class="profile-photo"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="김지예 프로필 일러스트"></div>
        <dl class="profile-mini-facts">
          <div><dt>Name</dt><dd>김지예 · Kim Ji Ye</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Birth</dt><dd>2001.01.02</dd></div>
